00:10.277 --> 00:11.820
Hope you enjoy this morning sermon.

00:13.002 --> 00:21.295
Because hope is one of those things that should be one of the keystones in every message, in every church, every Sunday, is that there's hope.

00:23.239 --> 00:24.200
