01:57.250 --> 02:07.924
And I just, not only for the sake of the church this morning, but the sake of people that watch on television and watch on the internet, I just want to remind us this morning what our message of hope is.

02:08.966 --> 02:14.754
First of all, I want to talk to you that God has given us hope for our past.

02:17.077 --> 02:26.930
